How are you feeling? Are you chilly?

44
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:50,970
I'm feeling a lot better
all thanks to an amazing doctor.

45
00:04:50,970 --> 00:04:56,600
Oh, being called an amazing doctor won't
make me feel happy or anything, you jerk.

46
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,440
He sure does look happy.

47
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,440
Yeah.

48
00:04:58,440 --> 00:05:00,270
Take it easy, Robin.

49
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:05,170
Don't feel pressured just because Luffy is up
and about after experiencing the same thing.

50
00:05:05,170 --> 00:05:07,160
It's okay to take your time and rest.

